text: First time on the market for this custom designed 2015 Marlette home, located in the highly desirable Portal Creek Park, an age 55+ community. The exceptional floorplan features 2 bedrooms, 2 baths, an office, a laundry room with extra storage/sink and an oversized 2 car garage with plenty of room for your RV or boat! A beautiful, fully fenced backyard adjacent to a wooded area, provides one of the most private lots in the community and plenty of shady comfort from your back patio. The only owners have meticulously maintained the home and has desirably features such as extra insulation in the walls, insulated plumbing and a highly efficient heat pump A/C system. Come see worry free living at its finest!

Custom home is on 2.51 acres of nature completed in Q4 2022. No steps throughout the home for true single level living. Custom features are extensive and numerous: 8' tall solid fir doors, 8' tall custom cherry/art glass front door, solid natural cherry kitchen cabinets in the large gourmet kitchen, oversized walk in pantry, stone core 100% waterproof luxury laminate floors. Open concept living, dining and kitchen. 7.1 surround sound wired living room, 120 motorized ALR projection screen that disappears when not in use. Hide-away lighted display area for valuable collections (whiskey not included). Workshop space in heated garage. 30x60x16 shop built in 2023. Enjoy the hummingbirds from the patio. Full 50A RV hookup No HOA, and more!

The Ivy by MainVue Homes at Horizon is a stunning design you do not want to miss. Upon entry find a soaring Two-Story Foyer a corner set a Home Office. Deeper into the home, the Two-Story Great Room is paired perfectly with a sophisticated Dining room and mutually connected Gourmet Kitchen flush with 3cm Quartz counters, Stainless Steel Appliances, and a Grand Butlers Pantry. For even more space, a main floor Multi-Purpose Room is tucked just off the kitchen. Upstairs, look out onto the Great Room from the front-facing Leisure room that leads to three secondary bedrooms and the luxurious Grand Suite. Customer registration policy: Buyers Broker to visit or be registered on Buyers 1st visit for full Commission is reduced.

Look no further for the perfect home or year round vacation property. This meticulously maintained, nicely updated home sits on a quiet cul-de-sac in the private, gated community of Mount Baker Rim. This welcoming, single story home features a spacious kitchen with a live edge counter and cork floors, guest bathroom with tiled walk in shower, primary suite with attached full bath, and newer laminate flooring throughout. There is a wood burning fireplace and a ductless heating/cooling system. It sits on a full slab foundation and has a wrap around deck with hot tub. There is a storage building and Studio/multi use building. Close to wonderful hiking, biking, and skiing. Gated community clubhouse, pool & more. $1000 annual dues.

Experience unparalleled coastal living in this completely redone home in picturesque Birch Bay! With breathtaking bay views from every part of the property, this high-quality residence has been entirely renovated inside & out, incl new electrical, plumbing, flooring, framing, decking, siding, roofing, insulation, paint, kitchen, bath, & laundry. Enjoy stunning vistas that enhance its luxurious finishes. Ample parking includes 2 assigned spaces & guest parking. Live full-time or vacation just minutes from the beach in this vibrant beachfront community, perfect for beach walks, clamming, crabbing, waterslides, dining, & shopping. Indoor cats & friendly dogs are welcome, ensuring everyone can enjoy the coastal paradise of Birch Bay.

One-owner home waits for new steward on the trails of south Alabama Hill. Faithfully maintained for 50+ years by the descendants of Bellingham founders, this 1-level home has had the hard work done-- you just get to choose colors. Newer roof, ext paint, furnace & H2o, kitchen appliances, windows & ext doors, plumbing fixtures, gas fireplace and electrical. Eat-in kitchen opens to the living room & to the den w/ sliders to the large, flat, sunny yard. Primary bedroom has walk-thru closet and continental access to the full bath. Lots of storage throughout including in the 2-car attached garage. Zero-traffic location at the intersection of two non-thru streets just steps from 240-acre Whatcom Falls Park. Trails literally in every direction.

Another great new home in Hannah Creek by Skeers Construction. Phase 5 is already more than half sold out! Gorgeous setting backs to a forested greenbelt with creek. Modern, great room floor plan features main floor primary and home office / flex room. Bonus room and two bedrooms on upper floor. Miles of trails to explore on the adjacent 3000 acre Galbraith Mountain trail system, and Whatcom Falls Park is just down the street. Feels like a world apart, but downtown is less than 3 miles away. Scheduled for end of August completion.

This immaculately maintained 3-bed, 2-bath home in Lynden offers the perfect blend of comfort, convenience, and security. With 1, 900 s.f. of living space, this home features a whole-house Natural Gas generator, a sprinkler system, security system, central A/C, high-end window coverings, updated flooring, updated appliances and much more. The large 11, 575 s.f. corner lot provides ample space for outdoor activities, while the fully fenced, manicured backyard offers a private oasis for outdoor living plus a custom-built workshop, gazebo, and hot tub covered by a pergola. Conveniently located across from the new Lynden Middle School, this home is an exceptional choice for folks seeking a peaceful, secure, and well-appointed living environment.

This ground-floor condo in the heart of Bellingham is a rare find at this price, offering a great opportunity for investors and first-time home buyers. The high ceilings enhance the spacious and inviting feel of this one-bedroom unit. Enjoy the private, covered back patio, which extends your living space. With secure parking, a courtyard, and elevator access, this condo ensures convenience and peace of mind. Your neighbors include Whole Foods Market, Civic Stadium, Bellingham Bells Ball Park, Arne Hanna Aquatic Center, Fred Meyer and Whatcom Falls Park. In Western Washington University bus line to boot. No rental cap!

This private property is perfectly situated to take in views of the surrounding mountains and amazing sunrises! Two parcels totaling 20 ac and abutting DNR land, an additional home could be built on the property. The freshly painted home has a professionally designed chef's kitchen, and has an abundance of cherry shaker cabinets with quartz countertops, a 5 burner gas Wolf cooktop and double wall ovens, as well as separate refrigerator and freezer (in the walk-in pantry). The living areas are all open and look to the mountains with vaulted ceilings and floor to ceiling windows. There's a 16'x32' in-ground pool, woodshed, 3 car garage, greenhouse, art studio and much more! Build another house and/or ADUs and enjoy the serenity and views.

Nestled up on King Mountain, this 2020 built home offers mesmerizing views of the bay, islands & city lights from your living room, primary bedroom & covered front deck. Enjoy the many upgrades including designer finishes of custom paint & high-end window coverings, air conditioning, oversized bedrooms, extra deep 2+ car garage wired for EV, and ample storage. Your back yard oasis abuts greenery and complete with covered deck & low maintenance turf. King Mountain is conveniently located near shopping, dining, entertainment, & medical services. For recreation, take advantage of the walking trails & parks throughout the area. Have peace of mind with this well cared for home. Simply unpack & relax, taking in sunset-painted skies each evening.

Situated in the sought after Columbia neighborhood, this single-level duplex is perched on West St with easy access to Squalicum Parkway. Embark on a leisurely walk to Squalicum Creek Park complete with a playground, off-leash dog park, sledding hills in the west corner of the park. Each unit has two beds and one bath and W&D. Find your way home in the well established Columbia neighborhood known for its walkability to downtown, parks, breweries and its peaceful, picturesque character year round.

Gorgeous two-story home located in the sought-after Semiahmoo neighborhood.This elegant home features a bright open living space, high ceilings, floor to ceiling stone gas fireplace, main floor large primary suite, top-down bottom-up blinds, and 2 mini split heating/cooling units. The kitchen has newer cabinetry, granite countertops with complete appliance update. Glass sliding doors off the dining area open to a private deck and beautiful park-like backyard. The laundry room has a newer washer and dryer with ample shelving for storage. The home is freshly painted inside and out.Upstairs youll find 2 bedrooms as well as a walk-in jacuzzi spa bath. This gorgeous home has been meticulously maintained with love and attention to detail.

Discover your peaceful oasis! Terrific mid county home on nearly of an acre 10 minutes to Bham or Lynden! The sprawling grounds are populated with mature fruit trees (cherry & apple), blueberry bushes, and privacy hedges. This 3-bedroom single level home is begging for your style & creativity. Its time to earn some sweat equity! Relax in the traditional floorplan w/tons of light, great storage, attached heated garage & workshop area. Dont stop there. Check out the multi-use shop of 1100 SF complete w/overhead lights, its own electrical box & great secured storage areas. Perfect for your home business! The circular driveway offers parking galore. This is a rare opportunity to create your dream country property so close to everything!

Fantastic southside location, walking distance from the historic Fairhaven area with eateries, groceries and every amenity one could need. Rare find! 2 remarkable homes 1 block away from Lake Whatcom! Live in one & rent the fully furnished ADU to subsidize your mortgage. Dining/living room is perfect for parties. Primary suite fts huge walk-in & en-suite w/artisan tile-work, walk-in shower & dual vanities. Upstairs rec room framed for 3rd bedroom/office. Grab a paddleboard & stroll to the neighborhood beach, walk to school, visit Stimpson Reserve or hop on a bike & shred Galbraith. SO much more, don't miss out!

Welcome to Malloy Terrace! This 2022 built home boasts modern finishes and thoughtful design, with plenty of space for everyone. Enjoy stepping into a large, open floor plan on the main level, offering an enormous great room coupled with a chef's kitchen with SS appliances, quartz countertops, and ample soft-close cabinetry. Entertaining is easy with the large living room and back deck that opens into the partially-fenced backyard. Primary bedroom suite comes w/ its own private bath, spacious walk-in closet & partial views. Laundry also conveniently located upstairs. Bask in breathtaking Mt Baker & N. Cascades views as you stroll through the community trails. This basically brand new home has so much to offer... Don't miss out on this one!

Nearly new, beautifully built & in excellent condition for your immediate move-in! This easy-to-own 4-yr-old home features an Open Layout w/spacious kitchen flowing to a dining area then family room w/a cozy gaslog fireplace! Primary BR on the main floor includes walk-in + en suite bath. Upstairs are 3 large guest BR's & full bath. The walk-out basement features a Rec Room for the main living area in one half, then an income-generating, legal, attached ADU that is vacant now but was just rented at $1600/mo. ADU has a full kitchen, laundry hook-ups, studio sleeping area & 3/4 bath. Separate entrance & parking make this set-up practical & profitable! B'ham's owner-occ. requirement ends with HB1337 & both units become rentable like a duplex.

Brand new townhome in Bellingham's Sunset Village community. This 3 story, 3 bedroom, 1.75 bath end unit features an oversized garage, stainless steel appliances, quartz countertops & mixed cabinetry. Walkable to shopping, dining, bus line, & trail system. Don't miss out on a great opportunity!

Experience the epitome of waterfront living at Sandy Point. This stunning 2, 976 sq ft home, built in 2018, boasts 3 bedrooms and 2.75 baths with an open floor plan thats perfect for entertaining. text: Cute 1965 single wide manufactured home on a double lot with a 1050 s.f. heated shop w/ half bath, accessed via alley behind! This one level 3 bed, 2 bath home features open concept living space which truly feels large. Primary bedroom with walk in closet, tiled flooring and backsplash w/ quartz countertops. Kitchen with stainless appliances, quarts countertops, full height backsplash tile & custom cabinets w/ addl pantry space in dining. Located close to schools, parks, restaurants, & the Canadian border. Hydroseed and landscaping in planter beds to be installed prior to closing and included in the purchase price. Vacant & move in ready!

Welcome to this quintessential Pacific Northwest craftsman on a quiet cul-de-sac in a well-established east-side neighborhood. Prepare to be greeted by a spacious living room with tall ceilings, a large kitchen & dining area that looks out to a fenced backyard, & a spacious covered patio, ideal for entertaining. This 2300+ home has a seamless flow & space for all, including 2 bedrooms on the main level, two bedrooms, & a bonus room upstairs. The main level primary suite offers a beautiful tiled walk-in shower & a large walk-in closet. Custom details include granite countertops, Knotty Alder solid core doors, trim & custom cabinets, an oversized garage, and a storage shed. Enjoy easy, comfortable living here.

Enjoy sunny days + great AC in this well-appointed Modern Farmhouse. The panoramic windows and vaulted ceilings show off gorgeous sunsets and endless natural light in the second-floor kitchen, dining + living rooms, and primary suite. The upgraded finishes include LVP flooring, quartz counters, & custom cabinetry. Energy-efficiency features include solar panels, tankless water heater, and mini-split systems for efficient heat + AC in the main living area & primary suite with HRV to keep the house well-ventilated. A view deck & fenced backyard provide outdoor entertainment options. Walkable + bikeable to many local trails & parks. Buy it furnished as a stylish second home or for easy moving. Come see it today!

Welcome to your dream lakeside retreat! Enjoy unparalleled privacy on the serene, less crowded end of the lake, perfect for peaceful escapes and unforgettable gatherings. Create lasting memories with water sports, marshmallow toasting, and fishing. The property features a charming creek, a main house with 3 bedrooms, 1.75 baths, 2 wood-burning fireplaces, a pool table, and a vintage bar. A separate cozy cabin offers a kitchen, laundry, bathroom, and outdoor BBQ space. A private dock and huge flat grassy area by the lake is ideal for games and relaxation. An extra lot adds over an acre of trees for seclusion. Enjoy quiet mornings and stunning sunsets, stargazing, and watching bald eagles' fish. Just a short drive to Bellingham and Seattle!

Discover the charm of Blaine in this beautifully maintained corner lot home, built in 2012, featuring fresh paint and new carpets. Providing a wonderful floor plan, this property includes a large primary bedroom conveniently located on the main floor. The kitchen flows seamlessly into the dining and living areas, perfect for entertaining. Upstairs, find sizable bedrooms accompanied by a full bath. Enjoy the privacy of a fully fenced backyard - ideal for gardening enthusiasts or pets. Situated near schools, downtown amenities, the bay, and with easy access to I-5. Better yet, no HOA!

An easy simple downsize for anyone seeking quiet refuge & more time to do things that matter. Welcome home to a kinder, more carefree way to live. Ideal for nature lovers & golf enthusiasts. Perfectly situated--south-facing sunshine all day! Great design with vaulted ceilings & wonderful windows. This spaciously gracious home offers top-of-the-line finishes, gas fireplace, stainless appliances, excellent exterior decks & lots of storage. Walking distance to all amenities-a best value property!

Welcome home to your single level, immaculately maintained, 3 bed 2 ba home with a flat driveway just inside Gate 3. Updated throughout with an eye for detail & modern aesthetic that you'll appreciate. Open layout for socializing in the newly renovated kitchen complete with modern cabinetry + incredible storage, quartz countertops, deep stainless sink & penny tile backsplash. New roof and all five skylights in 2022 + range in 2023. High eff. furnace + Heat pump & A/C, hardie siding, solid floors & white paint throughout. Great room style layout opens to trex deck over looking a gated sunny garden space. Generous and bright primary bed w/ ensuite double sink bath + 2 closets & private access to the deck. Tall crawl space for endless storage!

One of the best priced homes in Whatcom County! Cozy 1 bedroom cottage on a quiet cul de sac. Home will require some TLC but has great potential and room for your finishing touches. Private lot with shop space and shed for storage. Embrace rustic tranquility out in Maple Falls!

Contemporary and eco-friendly, NEW Larrabee Springs Venture Townhomes feature, 8 panel solar system, 2 bedrooms, 1.5 bathrooms, and modern design flooded with natural light. Explore the convenience of sidewalks and sustainable living with solar panels & EV wiring. Elevate the living experience with locally crafted cabinets by the renowned Highcraft Cabinets in Ferndale. Discover the perfect blend of style, functionality, and artisanal quality in these thoughtfully designed townhomes. Showings available between 12-3pm, 7dys a week. Larrabee Springs Venture Townhomes

Recently updated 3 bedroom plus an office room home with lots of off-street parking. New kitchen with quartz countertops, stainless steel appliances, and luxury vinyl plank throughout the home. Partial fence around the home. Spacious shed in the back for storage. As well as the corner of the property with mature trees . SandyPoint amenities include: pool, golf, marina, tennis, playground and clubhouse. Seller is offering $10k for closing costs and the sewer assessment has been paid off in full!

Architecturally exciting, contemporary 3 bed. home on coveted west side w/ sweeping water & island westerly views! This gorgeous home offers everything in one package; sustainability, luxury & access to the water & outer islands just one block from home (professionally installed mooring buoy to convey with sale). A plethora of very recent upgrades include; all windows ('23), siding('23), commercial-grade carpet ('23), Swedish firebox ('23), solar panel installation ('23), heat-pump &mini-splits throughout home ('23), new roof ('21). This home has nearly zero cost energy-wise with the solar electric connected to the heating systems. Automatic generator w/dedicated propane tanks. Plus, one car garage with workshop + addl' storage building.
nearby_schools: Lummi High School, Ferndale School District, Lummi Elementary School

text: Turn key, charming ground-level condo with Mt. Baker Views! Welcome to this spacious and wall-maintained 2-bed 1-bath condo, perfectly positioned on the ground floor with no stairs for easy access. The large windows flood the home with natural light, creating a bright and inviting atmosphere. Featuring a stunning Mt. Baker view from the back patio. Newer carpet and paint throughout. Enjoy the breathtaking sunrise views and the calming breeze from the patio. Convenient covered carport and storage directly in front of the front door. Private front patio deck and back patio space. Excellent location in the active and accessible community of Ferndale, just minutes from downtown!

Relax, renew, refresh at the Tides! This single-level home represents Birch Bay living at its finest. Close to the beach, restaurants, breweries and other amenities. Enjoy morning coffee in the sun on your front patio, gas fireplace to cozy up next to with a cup of cocoa in the cooler months, private driveway, open concept living with vaulted ceilings, custom shelving modifications, in-unit washer/dryer. This home is uniquely configured with no shared living space walls for maximum privacy. The Tides community provides ample parking, bay views, private storage, gas stub for BBQ, pool & hot tub access, clubhouse with kitchen, and game room. Enjoy relaxing walks to the beach and exploring the local C Shop.

Welcome home to the Crown Jewel of Galbraith! This is a once in a lifetime opportunity to own one of the best properties Bellingham has to offer. Perfectly appointed with incredible privacy, your own private pond, and a large shop for all your toys equipped with its own bath and plumbed for shower addition, fireplace, huge solar panel array and loft area. Enjoy gorgeous views from anywhere inside or outside no matter what time of the year. Less than a one minute ride to Galbraith, this is a mountain biker's dream. Near Lake Padden and within short driving distance to Fairhaven and downtown Bellingham. Thoughtfully designed to create up to 2 MIL suites or ADUs within the existing home, with minimal effort. This property has it all!

Welcome to Glenhaven Lakes; a vibrant, active community. Tastefully updated home perched atop a hill surrounded by lush greenery & mature trees for a peaceful atmosphere. Ground level offers: Versatile room for your office/hobbies, convenient laundry rm w/ bthrm & a spacious bonus room w/ a propane stove. Upper floor: Open concept kitchen, dining & south facing living room w/ tons of natural light. Spacious primary bdrm, full bthrm & walk-in closet. There are 2 other bdrms & another full bthrm. Move in ready w/ new carpet & laminate flrs. Durable metal roof too. Expansive, partially covered front deck & a small private deck out back. You will love the use of the pool, sport court, clubhouse, trails & parks. Easy commute to I-5 too!

Captivating bay & island views from this 2016-built Samish Hill craftsman. Originally constructed as a builder's own home, you'll notice exceptional workmanship and extra bells & whistles throughout. Open concept layout on the main level with an entertainer's kitchen showcasing a leathered quartzite island, soft-close cabinets, stainless steel appliances, quartz countertops and tile backsplash. Also on the main level is a bedroom/office with a 3/4 bathroom across the hall. Upstairs, you will find three additional bedrooms with vaulted ceilings. On the lower level, a 675 SQFT bonus room with wet bar. An oversized 2-car garage allows space for storage or a workshop. The trail behind the home provides quick access to Lake Padden.

Charming vintage Craftsman home lovingly preserved with it's timeless period finishes including unique fir floors, mouldings & light fixtures. Relax in open living & dining room with new wood-burning fireplace(heats the whole house) and custom tilework made in Michigan. Remodeled bathroom nods to the past with claw foot tub with shower head.Kitchen is charming with a new vintage Heartland stove and colorful marmoleum floor.Front bedroom has a walk-in closet that could be converted into ensuite bathroom. Detached 2 car garage has additional 264 square feet of finished space with heat and A/C-currently office & work out room.10 year old roof.New electrical panel.2018 furnace.Laundry in basement but could be located on back covered porch.

Contemporary and eco-friendly, NEW Larrabee Springs Venture Townhomes feature, 8 panel solar system, 2 bedrooms, 1.5 bathrooms, and modern design flooded with natural light. Explore the convenience of sidewalks and sustainable living with solar panels & EV wiring. Elevate the living experience with locally crafted cabinets by the renowned Highcraft Cabinets in Ferndale. Discover the perfect blend of style, functionality, and artisanal quality in these thoughtfully designed townhomes. Showings available between 12pm-3pm, 7 days a week. Larrabee Springs Venture Townhome

Welcome to your idyllic home tucked on the end of Clipper Rd. The main home has two bedrooms, a loft, a sunroom and a detached carport. Bask in the beautiful mountain views from the large deck, perfect for entertaining guests. A short drive down the road leads you to a quaint cabin that sits on a lower, large plot surrounded by garden space and across from a spacious shop for all your toys. The one bedroom cabin offers the second wood stove, and is perfect for guests, or a private studio. Opportunity to rent the cabin long term or potential short term rentals. A washer and dryer is located in the shop. Enjoy 6 acres enveloped by firs, cedars and mature landscaping. This property offers privacy and tranquility while overlooking the valley.

This prime Southside home boasts an enviable location, excellent walkability, and numerous updates. The home features a bright, south-facing open kitchen and main living area. It's just an 8-minute walk to downtown Fairhaven's restaurants and shops, w/the Interurban Trail system, dog park, and Amtrak Station even closer. The functional layout includes 3bd, 2ba, and a laundry room on the upper level, w/1bd and 1ba on the lower level. The attached 2-car garage offers extensive cabinetry and workspace. Recent upgrades include a new roof, a 4 kW solar system, a heat pump w/AC, and fresh interior and exterior paint. A gardener's paradise with multiple raised beds, fruit trees, and berries. Backyard shed provides a home office or yoga studio.

This home sits on a gently sloped hillside with wonderful views of Birch Bay and Mt. Baker. Good sized corner lot with open views from almost every room. Spacious 3 bedrooms, 2 full bath, 200 Sf enclosed porch and 400 SF attached garage. 1974 manufactured home is in good condition. Ready to move in or to rented out. HOA dues are only $25/year. Very quite and friendly community. Listing agent is related to the Seller.

Sweet Happy Valley location, close to Fairhaven, schools, parks and the 100 Acre Woods Trails. Two-bedroom rambler on a large level lot offers a lot of potential for the right buyer. Three-quarter bath was remodeled for handicap access. Stairs lead to additional square footage with lower ceiling height (appx 5'10 ) for storage which is not included in the appx. square feet. Definitely a cosmetic fixer, but the home is well placed for additional development. Gas forced air heat, all appliances included, large utility room & 1 car carport. Close to Western Washington State University!

Have you ever dreamed of owning a home with water and sunset views, then this home just might make your dreams come true! You can start each day with views of Bellingham Bay and the San Juan Islands, but end each one, with a kaleidoscope of multicolored sunset salt water views. Located in Edgemoor, one of our most desirable neighborhoods, this home features a chef's kitchen large enough for your closest 20 friends, vaulted ceilings throughout, 2 primary suites, a gym & yoga retreat, a private guest suite, two view decks, one being partially covered, right off the great room! This home is close and walkable to the Historical Fairhaven District, granting easy access to dining, shopping. and very close to the Chuckanut Mountain trail system!

Great opportunity to own this completely updated charming home. Spacious bright kitchen with lots cabinets for storage, large living room, new double pane windows, new flooring, new paint, new Led lighting, new decks, move in ready. All new appliances all include. Extra parking space, storage shed included. Located in a close distance to town amenities, grocery stores and downtown. Buyer must be approved by the park before closing. This is a Must see!!

Brand NEW Marlette home at Ponderosa Estates! Affordability and a gorgeous location minutes from Birch Bay! Appealing 23 acre park with a very northwest vibe. This new 3 bed, 2 bath home features a primary en-suite with spacious walk-in closet, dual sinks and ample storage. Bright contemporary kitchen with large pantry, gorgeous countertops with tile back splash and brand new stainless steel appliances. A spacious backyard where you can create your own garden and patio area. Watch the sunrise from your beautiful covered front porch. Take a walk down to the beach and enjoy cafes, restaurants, parks, trails and spectacular sunsets on the promenade. An all age year-round community.

Extraordinary brand new 3 bed, 2.75 bath custom-built home nestled on a sunny cul-de-sac lot, boasting mountain views. This home is designed for seamless entertaining with tons of extras, featuring a great open floor plan, vaulted wood ceiling, open stairway & a cozy wood-burning fireplace, metal roof & AC. The main floor offers spa like primary suite and second bedroom. Step outside to discover an oversized deck & luxurious hot tub, perfect for relaxation & gatherings. This property presents an opportunity to own a stunning glacier retreat near Mt. Baker & Nooksack River. Residents enjoy access to a clubhouse, tennis courts, play ground, river, pool, sauna & more. Experience the best of mountain living in this remarkable home.

This home is located in Fairhaven's Parkway Village 55 and better active community. If you have been looking for a community to connect w/ and experience all that South Bellingham has to offer, this is it! Come look at this 3 bdrm, 2 bthrm single-level home w/ an attached carport and storage area. You will enjoy the south-facing sunny deck or the covered patio located just off the dining room. The kitchen is light and bright w/a skylight, updated kitchen cabinets and stainless steel appliances. The home has been well taken care of w/ lots of significant updates like a newer furnace and A/C system, new windows, and a new water heater (a complete list is available). There are established garden beds and a fully fenced backyard space to enjoy.

Don't miss this onepriced to sell! Welcome to this spacious four-bedroom, two-and-a-half-bathroom home situated in a charming neighborhood. This property features a generous layout with a primary bedroom conveniently located on the main floor. Enjoy the added benefit of a public park just off the backyard, perfect for outdoor activities and relaxation.

Discover serenity at Festival Boulevard, Bellingham's top 55+ enclave. Nestled in the vibrant Cordata community, this charming condominium boasts vaulted ceilings and expansive windows, bathing the space in natural light. Enjoy a spacious deck and detached garage for ample storage. Adjacent to scenic trails, shopping, medical services, and the new Cordata Park, this retreat offers the perfect blend of convenience and tranquility. Welcome home.
